{"tid":637964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我可以證明哩個世界無外星人！","createTime":"2018-04-22T09:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T05:44:05.000Z","uid":181416,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"041c3fdefd6bf4b552b752f98e60ae788c5e36e7","tid":637964,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"我要同大家講一個事實，<br />\n比少少時間我，有啲長，<br />\n外國有好多電影都係講外星人，<br />\n星球大戰、星空奇遇記啊，<br />\n人人都應該有睇過下，<br />\n捉咗地球人去做實驗啊，<br />\n左右鄰居其實係外星人啊<br />\n，太多哩啲科幻電影喇，<br />\n救救你哋嘅下一代，<br />\n命中注定人類係孤獨<br />\n！！根本就無外星人！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ba81b0204cdb24e2df3097d890fae255773016","tid":637964,"uid":76399,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"低質藏頭詩"},{"pid":"ed15e2a9306c749e3278eac08af5fa0b8c11b3f0","tid":637964,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"點救下一代?"},{"pid":"0af72d2617922442794cfbc937926870528aec8a","tid":637964,"uid":163842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"唔好勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be70d876462c52a0844ba4a50aec77f464a286a","tid":637964,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:49:16.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6734bce5ad2f2583ff74c5f7bc9508fe19dc4640","tid":637964,"uid":181416,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed15e2a9306c749e3278eac08af5fa0b8c11b3f0","tid":637964,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:47:07.000Z","msg":"點救下一代?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"係媒體報導番無外星人，<br />\n太易令下一代有幻想唔係好事，<br />\n平行時空哩啲題